flowchart TD
    A[Select highest-priority item\nP0 typed frontend API layer] --> B[Implement src/frontend/src/utils/api.ts]
    B --> C[Add typed clients\nloadInternalData + runAgent]
    C --> D[Add deterministic error mapping\nhttp | timeout | network | malformed_response]
    D --> E[Add unit tests\napi.test.ts]
    E --> F[Attempt required fresh Docker cycle]
    F --> G{Docker daemon accessible?}
    G -- No --> H[BLOCKED: docker socket permission denied]
    H --> I[Document blocker in IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md\nwith failed command + next action]

    J[Key decisions] --> J1[Return ApiResult<T> union instead of throwing]
    J --> J2[Runtime response guards prevent UI crashes on malformed payloads]
